  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ColumnMetadata
    Interface that describes the metadata associated to each column.
    Configuration
    Interface that describes information about the environment and numbers and types of links connected to this stage.
    DataChannel
    Interface that transfers data between the conductor node and the player nodes.
    InputLink
    Interface for manipulating incoming Record objects.
    InputRecord
    Interface for manipulating an incoming record.
    Link
    Interface for manipulating incoming or outgoing Record objects.
    OutputLink
    Interface for manipulating outgoing Record objects.
    OutputRecord
    Interface for manipulating an outgoing stream record.
    Record
    Base interface for the representation of a row data on the link.
    RejectRecord
    Interface for manipulating an outgoing reject record.
